The '''Masterball''' is a type of pokeball. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if and is the highest type of pokeball avaliable.


==Details==
===Description===
The Ultimate pokeball to capture Pokémon with. It has an 100% catch rate. Each time it is purchased it is 35% more expensive, capping at 100 times the base price

